        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-14T11:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-14T11:00:00-05:00" n="242" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d242">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 PW/7–1445: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 242<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_WJG2" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">u. s. urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-14T12:00:00-04:00">July 14, 1945—noon.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5773. Ital Ambassador has informed <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss>
                    <persName corresp="#p_I2">Italy</persName> has declared war against <persName corresp="#p_J1">Japan</persName> and that declaration will be made public
                    July 15. <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> therefore proposes to announce on
                    July 17 this Govt’s intention to support officially <persName corresp="#p_I2">Italy</persName>’s admission in due course to world security
                    organization.</p>
                <p>Inform Foreign Office urgently of <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss>’s
                    intention and express hope that British Govt will support American position.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GJC1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
